| `red-cell-c2-f6o2` | P2 — Concurrent `encrypt_for_agent` calls may race on CTR counter |
| `red-cell-c2-tc5q` | P3 — `restore_running` with port-in-use failure state not tested |
| `red-cell-c2-d53r` | P3 — `ListenerManager::create` duplicate name rejection not tested |
