**Most critical gap**: The beacon output File/FileWrite/FileClose download lifecycle (`red-cell-c2-lgcr`, P2) — this is the core path by which agent-exfiltrated files arrive, get reassembled, and get persisted as loot. A regression here could silently drop or corrupt downloaded files with zero test coverage to catch it.

