**Injection status handlers** (`handle_inject_shellcode_callback`, `handle_inject_dll_callback`, `handle_spawn_dll_callback`) — these are security-critical functions that report whether shellcode/DLL injection succeeded. An operator makes tactical decisions based on this feedback. Zero tests exist for any of these handlers. Filed as P2.

